#String tooltip
This bot burns bone material into bone ash using kilns. You need an area with 'kiln' specialization for kilns and 'boneforash' specialization for input piles with bone material. The bot will fill kilns, add branch fuel, light them, wait for burning to complete, and collect bone ash. It will continue automatically until no more bones are available.
